# Local-only secrets for the private Runtime Worker (`insecur-runtime`), loaded by `wrangler dev`.
# Copy to apps/runtime/.dev.vars and fill in. Never commit real secrets.
#
# The Runtime Worker is the ONLY deploy that holds the root key (INSTANCE_ROOT_KEY_V1, bound from
# Secrets Store, not set here). It has no public routes and no WorkOS bindings. It verifies the
# scoped hop token the API Worker forwards (ADR-0077).
#
# Deployed/preview environments deliver RUNTIME_TOKEN_SIGNING_SECRET via encrypted Worker secrets
# (`wrangler secret put` or `--secrets-file`), not plaintext wrangler `vars` (INS-276).

# HMAC secret shared with the API Worker to verify the scoped hop token. Must match the value in
# apps/api/.dev.vars (RUNTIME_TOKEN_SIGNING_SECRET). Must be at least 32 characters.
RUNTIME_TOKEN_SIGNING_SECRET=

# Optional local Sentry error reporting. DSNs are public, but keep local files ignored.
SENTRY_DSN=
SENTRY_ENVIRONMENT=local
